Verses rhythmic :

    Pompe Brassens : index 3rd string, middle 2nd string, annular 1st string.

    Thumb : Switch between two strings, the 5th and the 6th strings. For B7 and C add finger on the

6th string

             at the same fret as the string below.

            For E7 you can strum in the reverse order, 6th string before 5th string

 

[Intro]
   A C E A G  E G F#  D  F E D C B A

